
This is the ElasTool software & test suite

 * COPYRIGHT: the license of under which ElasTool can be distributed
 * README: This file
 * doc: Users' Manual
 * src: The source code; please see also the file 'INSTALL'
 * examples: Example inputs 
 * tools: Some small programs/scripts needed to analyze the results


Bugs and suggestions can be sent to zl.liu@163.com or cekuma1@gmail.com.

If you find something interesting that will be published, please cite ElasTool as,

Zhong-Li Liu and Chinedu Ekuma, ElasTool: An automated Python-based toolkit for calculating elastic constants. 
